  Features of MUICode
  ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
  
   * MUICode enables to code and decode text files using the Vigénčre Grid
     coding method. The coding key is limited to five digits.
        
   * Uses the great @{"MUI" link "MUI" 0} !
@endnode

