@endnode

@node "Introduction" "Introduction"
@next "Legal"
@prev "Installation"


                             MUICode V1.0
                             ~~~~~~~~~~~~

  Introduction
  ~~~~~~~~~~~~
  
  @{"I" link "Author" 0} created MUICode in order to get familiar with the great @{"MUI" link "MUI" 0}.
  MUICode is a software which enables to code and decode text files
  (if you try to code or decode a file of a different type, the 
  program won't crash, but you won't get the awaited result).
  The coding method used is the Vigénčre Grid method. This method is a 
  quite simple method using a coding key (limited to five digits) and, as its
  name indicates, a symbol grid. In a textfile, only the letters and numbers
  will be coded (the others symbols will remain the same).
@endnode

